    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to put this beauty up for sale, but it's time for her to find a new home where she'll be truly appreciated. I've babied this car since day one\u2014she's been garage-kept, hand-washed, and treated like a member of the family. You\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish; she still looks and smells like she just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s an absolute dream to drive, smooth as silk and turns heads at every corner. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for by a true enthusiast who knows their stuff, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, let's chat cars, and see if she's the right fit for your garage!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
