      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! It truly breaks my heart to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new owner to enjoy what is essentially a showroom-fresh dream. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it with hand-washes every weekend. It\u2019s in such stunning shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the assembly line. It drives smooth as silk and has that 'new car' magic that\u2019s hard to find. I\u2019d love for you to swing by, grab a coffee, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one. You won't find a more loved or better-kept ride around!",
      "price": 46500.0,
